msgid ""
"In some cases, you might need to change the state for a user other than "
"the one who triggered the current handler. For example, you might want to"
" change the state of a user based on an admin's command."
msgstr ""

#: ../../dispatcher/finite_state_machine/index.rst:98
msgid ""
"To do this, you can use the ``get_context`` method of the FSM middleware "
"through the dispatcher:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../dispatcher/finite_state_machine/index.rst:120
msgid ""
"This allows you to manage the state of any user in your bot, not just the"
" one who triggered the current handler."
msgstr ""

